replaceStrings.replace: CONCAT(e.nom_equipe, ' (', c.nom, ') (', comp.libelle, ')' (', cl.division, ')') AS team_full_name,
CONCAT(e.nom_equipe, ' (', c.nom, ') (', comp.libelle, ') (', cl.division, ')') AS team_full_name,
FROM equipes e LEFT JOIN classements cl ON cl.id_equipe = e.id_equipe
CONCAT(e.nom_equipe, ' (', c.nom, ') (', comp.libelle, ')', IFNULL(CONCAT('(', cl.division, ')'), '')) AS team_full_name,
